{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"font semantic tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"multiple","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"composite","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or not, and expose them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllFontSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllFontSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic013FontCompositeB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic012FontMultipleB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic04FontB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider\/init()"],"title":"Initializers"},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider\/weightSystemMode